%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSponge%20Bombs%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel's%20New%20Secret%20Weapon%20To%20Block%20Hamas%20Tunnels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFighting%20in%20Gaza%20has%20entered%20day%2021%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20surprise%20cross-border%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20killing%20about%201%2C400%20people.%20Since%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20bombarding%20Gaza%2C%20in%20which%20more%20than%207%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20has%20also%20mounted%20an%20incursion%20deeper%20into%20Gaza%20on%20Friday%20as%20it%20readies%20for%20a%20ground%20offensive%20against%20Hamas.%20However%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20the%20Israeli%20troops%20face%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-updates-hamas-tunnel-warfare-and-lessons-for-israel-from-vietnam-war-al-qaeda-gaza-war-gaza-war-live-gaza-tunnels-4493256%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextensive%20Hamas%20tunnel%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20group%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20several%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20reportedly%20has%20different%20kinds%20of%20tunnels%20--%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20long%20and%20up%20to%2080%20metres%20deep%20--%20running%20beneath%20the%20sandy%20360-sq-km%20coastal%20strip%20and%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESponge%20bombs%C2%A0create%20sudden%20explosion%20of%20foam%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20fight%20Hamas%20through%20its%20tunnel%20network%2C%20Israel%20is%20reportedly%20making%20%26quot%3Bsponge%20bombs%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20create%20a%20sudden%20explosion%20of%20foam%20that%20rapidly%20expands%20and%20then%20hardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20testing%20the%20chemical%20grenades%2C%20which%20contain%20no%20explosives%20but%20ar