20of%20133.47.%20His%20tally%20includes%20one%20blazing%20century%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20a%20half-century%20against%20Pakistan.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20also%20has%20the%20most%20sixes%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20with%2017%20of%20his%20hits%20going%20out%20of%20the%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20contender%20for%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament%20award%2C%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20is%20batting%20like%20a%20dream%20at%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023.%20De%20Kock%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20retire%20from%20ODIs%20after%20this%20tournament%2C%20has%20already%20smashed%20three%20centuries%20and%20has%20accumulated%20407%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2081.40%20and%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20114.97.%20His%20three%20centuries%20so%20far%20have%20come%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Australia%20and%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Virat%20Kohli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20often%20hailed%20as%20the%20king%20of%20run%20chases%2C%20is%20living%20up%20to%20that%20prestigious%20title%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament.%20With%20354%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%2C%20he%20is%20second%20only%20to%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20in%20the%20run-scoring%20charts.%20Kohli%20is%20averaging%20a%20staggering%20118%20so%20far%20and%20is%20batting%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%2090.53.%20In%20the%20five%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20one%20century%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20three%20half-centuries%2C%20missing%20out%20on%20a%2050%2B%20score%20only%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Pakistan%20have%20had%20a%20disappointing%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20Mohammad%20Rizwan's%20exploits%20with%20the%20bat%20have%20been%20a%20redeeming%20feature.%20With%20302%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2075.50%2C%20Rizwan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20five%20run-scorers%20in%