20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happens%20to%20be%20Indian%20foreign%20military%20presence%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20head%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20archipelago%2C%20said%20in%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%20to%20Bloomberg%20TV.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20reaction%20would%20be%20the%20same%20if%20the%20troops%20were%20of%20any%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%2070%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20maintain%20New%20Delhi-sponsored%20radar%20stations%20and%20surveillance%20aircrafts.%20Indian%20warships%20help%20patrol%20Maldives'%20exclusive%20economic%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20said%20he%20has%20already%20begun%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20on%20removing%20its%20military%20presence%2C%20calling%20those%20talks%20%26quot%3Bvery%20successful%20already.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20a%20bilateral%20relationship%20that's%20mutually%20beneficial%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Indian%20soldiers%20won't%20be%20replaced%20by%20troops%20from%20other%20countries.%20Asking%20India%20to%20remove%20military%20personnel%20no%20way%20indicates%20%26quot%3Bthat%20I'm%20going%20to%20allow%20China%20or%20any%20other%20country%20to%20bring%20their%20military%20troops%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuizzu's%20win%20extends%20the%20tug-of-war%20between%20China%20and%20India%20for%20influence%20over%20the%20strategically%20located%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Successive%20governments%20have%20tilted%20either%20toward%20India%20or%20China.%20Both%20Asian%20powerhouses%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20upgrading%20Maldives%20infrastructure%20and%20extended%20loans%2C%20as%20they%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20such%20as%20Japan%20and%20Australia%20are%20looking%20to%20isolate%20an%20increasingly%20assertive%20and%20assured%20Beijing%20and%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20propping-up%20New%20Delhi%20as%20a%20regional%20counterweight%20and%20key%20partner%20in%20Asia.%20That%20seemed%20to%20pay%20off%20as%20Muizzu's%20predecessor%2C%20Solih%20steered%20the%20country%20closer%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Cooperation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20now%20promises%20to%20change%20tack%20by%20removing%20India%20troops%20and%20addressing%20the%20adverse%20trade%20balance%20with%20the%20South%20Asian%20neighbor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20assistance%2C%20cooperation%20with%20all%20the%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%20said%2C%20dismissing%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20elections%20were%20a%20referendum%20on%20closer%20ties%20with%20either%20China%20or%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2045-year-old%20engineer%20turned%20mayor%20of%20Male%2C%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20and%20one-time%20housing%20minister%2C%20leads%20a%20party%20that%20welcomed%20Chinese%20loans%20and%20oversaw%20a%20wide-ranging%20crackdown%20on%20dissent%20when%20it%20was%20last%20in%20power%20about%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20nation%20of%20just%20over%20500%2C000%20people%2C%20spread%20over%20187%20inhabited%20islands%2C%20is%20a%20tourist%20destination%20and%20in%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20archipelago%20also%20sits%20along%20busy%20shipping%20routes%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20which%20has%20long%20played%20the%20role%20of%20regional%20power%2C%20for%20it's%20part%2C%20says%20it%20intends%20to%20work%20with%20the%20new%20Maldives%20government%2C%20even%20as%20it%20watches%20Muizzu's%20moves%20warily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20constructively%20engaging%20with%20the%20incoming%20administration%20and%20discussing%20ways%20to%20enhance%20our%20relationship%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20Arindam%20Bagchi%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20told%20reporters%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20specifically%20about%20the%20maritime%20securi