nnel%20dug%20from%20Gaza%20to%20Israel%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20soldier%20keeps%20guard%20next%20to%20an%20entrance%20to%20what%20the%20Israeli%20military%20say%20is%20a%20cross-border%20attack%20tunnel%20dug%20from%20Gaza%20to%20Israel%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fdo4seok_hamas-tunnel-city-_625x300_27_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20soldier%20keeps%20guard%20next%20to%20an%20entrance%20to%20what%20the%20Israeli%20military%20say%20is%20a%20cross-border%20attack%20tunnel%20dug%20from%20Gaza%20to%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20believes%20that%20with%20Israel's%20overwhelming%20aerial%20and%20armoured%20military%20superiority%2C%20tunnels%20are%20a%20way%20to%20cut%20some%20of%20those%20advantages%20by%20forcing%20Israel's%20soldiers%20to%20move%20underground%20in%20cramped%20spaces%20the%20Hamas%20fighters%20know%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20Thursday%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20elaborate%20on%20the%20number%20of%20kilometres%20of%20tunnels%20but%20it%20is%20a%20high%20number%2C%20built%20under%20schools%20and%20residential%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20to%20intervene%2C%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20%26quot%3Baggression%26quot%3B%20on%20Gaza%20and%20moves%20toward%20%26quot%3Ba%20political%20solution%20instead%20of%20military%20and%20security%20solutions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUNDERGROUND%20CITY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20security%20sources%20say%20Israel's%20heavy%20aerial%20bombardments%20have%20caused%20little%20damage%20to%20the%20tunnel%20infrastructure%20with%20Hamas%20naval%20commandos%20able%20to%20launch%20a%20seaborne%20attack%20targeting%20coastal%20communities%20near%20Gaza%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20we%20have%20been%20attacking%20massively%20for%20days%20and%20days%2C%20the%20(Hamas)%20leadership%20is%20pretty%20much%20intact%2C%20as%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20command%20and%20control%2C%20the%20ability%20even%20to%20try%20and%20launch%20counter%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amir%20Avivi%2C%20a%20former%20brigadier%20general%20whose%20senior%20positions%20in%20the%20Israeli%20military%20included%20deputy%20commander%20of%20the%20Gaza%20division%2C%20tasked%20with%20tackling%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20whole%20city%20all%20over%20Gaza%20underneath%20with%20depths%20of%2040-50%20metres.%20There%20are%20bunkers%20and%20headquarters%20and%20storage%20and%20of%20course%20they%20are%20connected%20to%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20rocket%20launching%20positions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20sources%20estimated%20depths%20of%20up%20to%2080%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20Western%20security%20source%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20run%20for%20miles.%20They%20are%20made%20of%20concrete%20and%20very%20well%20made.%20Think%20of%20the%20Viet%20Cong%20times%2010.%20They%20have%20had%20years%20and%20lots%20of%20money%20with%20which%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20security%20source%2C%20from%20one%20of%20Israel's%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20said%20Hamas's%20tunnels%20from%20Egypt%20remain%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supply%20chain%20is%20still%20intact%20these%20days.%20The%20network%20involved%20in%20facilitating%20co-ordination%20are%20some%20Egyptian%20military%20officers.%20It%20is%20unclear%20if%20there%20is%20knowledge%20of%20this%20by%20the%20Egyptian%20army%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20small%20number%20of%20narrower%2C%20deep%2C%20smuggling%20tunnels%20were%20still%20operating%20until%20recently%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20two%20security%20sources%20and%20a%20trader%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20city%20of%20El%20Arish%2C%20but%20they%20had%20slowed%20to%20a%20near-halt%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgyptian%20officials%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20said%20while%20inspecting%20military%20units%20in%20Suez%20that%20the%20army's%20role%20was%20to%20secure%20Egyptian%20borders.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fsite%3Dclassic%26id%3D734593%26autostart%3Dfalse%26autoplay%3D0%26pWidth%3D650%26pHeight%3D400%26category%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELONG%20GAME%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20was%20created%20in%20Gaza%20in%201987%20and%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20begun%20digging%20tunnels%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%20when%20Israel%20granted%20Yasser%20Arafat's%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organization%20some%20degree%20of%20self-rule%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20network%20is%20a%20key%20reason%20why%20Hamas%20is%20stronger%20in%20Gaza%20than%20in%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20Israel's%20settlements%2C%20military%20bases%20and%20monitoring%20devices%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20get%20anything%20in%20from%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETunneling%20became%20easier%20in%202005%20when%20Israel%20pulled%20its%20soldiers%20and%20settlers%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20when%20Hamas%20won%20power%20in%20a%202006%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterwards%20Hamas's%20military%20wing%2C%20the%20Izz%20el-Deen%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20captured%20Gilad%20Shalit%20and%20killed%20two%20other%20Israeli%20soldiers%20after%20burrowing%20600%20metres%20to%20raid%20the%20Kerem%20Shalom%20base%20on%20the%20Gaza%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20military%20strike%20against%20Arafat's%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20using%20tunnel-mounted%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20military%20tunnels%20remained%20off-limits%20to%20outside%20eyes%2C%20during%20that%20era%20Gaza%20smugglers%20would%20show%20off%20their%20scarcely%20concealed%20commercial%20tunnels%20under%20the%20Rafah%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20were%20around%20three%20feet%20(one%20metre)%20wide%20and%20used%20winch%20motors%20to%20haul%20goods%20along%20the%20sandy%20tunnel%20floors%20in%20hollowed-out%20petrol%20barrels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20Rafah%20tunnel%20operator%2C%20Abu%20Qusay%2C%20said%20a%20half-mile%20tunnel%20took%20three%20to%20six%20months%20to%20dig%20and%20could%20yield%20profits%20of%20up%20to%20%24100%2C000%20a%20day.%20The%20most%20profitable%20item%20was%20bullets%2C%20bought%20for%20%241%20each%20in%20Egypt%20and%20fetching%20more%20than%20%246%20in%20Gaza.%20Kalashnikov%20rifles%2C%20he%20said%2C%20cost%20%24800%20in%20Egypt%20and%20sold%20for%20twice%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202007%20the%20military%20wing%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20brought%20its%20commander%20Mohammed%20Deif%20into%20Gaza%20through%20a%20tunnel%20from%20Egypt.%20Deif%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20Hamas's%20deadly%20Oct.%207%20attack%20into%20Israel%2C%20which%20killed%201%2C400%20people%20and%20hostages%20were%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETUNNEL%20HUNTING%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Joel%20Roskin%2C%20a%20geomorphologist%20and%20geologist%20with%20Israel's%20Bar-Ilan%20University%20said%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20map%20the%20tunnel%20network%20accurately%20from%20the%20surface%20or%20space%2C%20adding%20highly%20classified%20information%20was%20essential%20for%203D%20mapping%20and%20imagery%20visualization.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20elite%20units%20tasked%20with%20going%20underground%20is%20Yahalom%2C%20specialist%20commandos%20from%20Israel's%20Combat%20Engineering%20Corps%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bweasels%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20specialise%20in%20finding%2C%20clearing%20and%20destroying%20the%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20visited%20Yahalom%20fighters%2C%20telling%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20rely%20on%20you%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20rely%20on%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20sources%20said%20what%20awaits%20them%20is%20formidable%20and%20they%20faced%20an%20enemy%20that%20has%20regrouped%20and%20learned%20from%20previous%20Israeli%20operations%20in%202014%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20booby%20traps.%20They%20have%20thermobaric%20weapons%20that%20they%20didn't%20have%20in%202021%2C%20which%20are%20more%20lethal.%20And%20I%20believe%20they%20acquired%20a%20lot%20of%20anti-tank%20weapon%20systems%20that%20are%20going%20to%20try%20to%20hit%20our%20APCs%20(armoured%20personnel%20carriers)%2C%20tanks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amnon%20Sofrin%2C%20a%20former%20brigadier%20general%20and%20former%20commander%20of%20the%20Combat%20Intelligence%20Corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESofrin%2C%20who%20was%20also%20previously%20head%20of%20the%20intelligence%20directorate%20with%20Israel's%20Mossad%20spy%20agency%2C%20said%20Hamas%20would%20also%20be%20trying%20to%20kidnap%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDaphne%20Richemond-Barak%2C%20professor%20at%20Israel's%20Reichman%20University%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20Underground%20Warfare%2C%20said%20the%20conflicts%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%20had%20changed%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20IDF%20(Israeli%20military)%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20inside%20the%20tunnels%20is%20also%20all%20of%20the%20experience%20and%20all%20of%20the%20knowledge%20that%20has%20been%20gained%20by%20groups%20like%20ISIS%20(Islamic%20State)%20and%20has%20been%20...%20passed%20on%20to%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20synd