20till%203%20a.m.%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BSF%2C%20which%20is%20mandated%20to%20guard%20the%203%2C323%20km%20India-Pakistan%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overnight%20shelling%20is%20the%20biggest%20ceasefire%20violation%20along%20the%20international%20border%20after%20ceasefire%20understanding%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20February%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20week%20ago%2C%20two%20BSF%20jawans%20were%20injured%20in%20Pakistani%20firing%20in%20Arnia%20sector.%20But%20situation%20was%20immediately%20brought%20under%20control%20after%20a%20flag%20meeting%20between%20local%20commanders%20of%20BSF%20and%20Rangers%20on%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocals%20say%20firing%20started%20at%208%20pm%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20loud%20explosions%20as%20mortar%20guns%20were%20used%20by%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20overnight%20shelling%20some%20residential%20houses%20were%20also%20hit.%20At%20least%20one%20residential%20house%20was%20damaged%20in%20the%20firing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20heavy%20shelling%20many%20villagers%20fled%20their%20homes%20and%20took%20shelter%20in%20safer%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698384600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F425nilm8_arnia-mortar-shell-by-pak_625x300_27_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-troops-fire-at-indian-posts-residential-areas-in-jammu-and-kashmir-arnia-4518106%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20personnel%20was%20injured%20in%20unprovoked%20firing%20and%20motor%20shelling%20in%20Arnia%20sector%20along%20the%20border%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Dozens%20of%20villagers%20have%20fled%20their%20homes%20after%20mortar%20shells%20hit%20residential%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-troops-fire-at-indian-posts-residential-areas-in-jammu-and-kashmir-arnia-4518106%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-troops-fire-at-indian-posts-residential-areas-in-jammu-and-kashmir-arnia-4518106%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-troops-fire-at-indian-posts-residential-areas-in-jammu-and-kashmir-arnia-4518106%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Tejas%20-%20An%20Air%20Combat%20Thriller%20Has%20Never%20Been%20So%20Airy-Fairy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%20think%20about%20the%20nation%20-%20that%20is%20the%20mantra%20that%20%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Sarvesh%20Mewara%20and%20produced%20by%20Ronnie%20Screwvala's%20RSVP%20Movies%2C%20harps%20upon.%20This%20is%20a%20film%20that%20religiously%20adheres%20to%20that%20axiom.%20It%20is%20always%20in%20doubt%20and%20it%20never%20lets%20the%20nation%20slip%20out%20of%20its%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20try%20as%20hard%20as%20it%20may%2C%20%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%20comes%20a%20complete%20cropper%20-%20it%20is%20a%20dead-on-arrival%20cinematic%20consignment%20that%20does%20no%20justice%20at%20all%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20or%20the%20medium.%20It%20is%20an%20insufferably%20bland%20thriller%20that%20believes%20that%20peddling%20patriotism%20can%20help%20it%20paper%20over%20its%20pockmarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToplined%20by%20a%20completely%20out%20of%20her%20depth%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20in%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20who%20thrives%20on%20dangerous%20missions%20and%20empty%20platitudes%2C%20%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20precariously%20low-flying%20vehicle%20that%20never%20gathers%20any%20velocity.%20It%20lurches%20from%20one%20crashlanding%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20have%20taken%20some%20doing%20for%20the%20makers%20to%20turn%20an%20aviation%20actioner%20into%20such%20a%20stilted%2C%20insipid%20affair.%20The%20excruciatingly%20vacuous%20writing%20-%20the%20lines%20that%20the%20characters%20spout%20are%20right%20out%20of%20a%20how-real-people-should-not-speak%20handbook%2C%20is%20aggravated%20manifold%20by%20the%20terribly%20sloppy%20acting%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERanaut's%20eponymous%20character%20is%20a%20'rockstar'%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20fighter%20pilot%20who%20flies%20the%20single-engine%20light%20combat%20aircraft%20that%20shares%20her%20name.%20Well%2C%20well%2C%20Tejas%20piloting%20a%20Tejas%20in%20a%20mission%20called%20Tejas%20in%20a%20film%20titled%20Tejas%20-%20how%20dramatic!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20has%20a%20scene%20in%20which%20the%20appeal%20of%20a%20popstar%20(Varun%20Mitra%2C%20who%20shows%20up%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20is%20projected%20as%20the%20heroine's%20romantic%20interest%20and%20then%20is%20seen%20no%20more%20because%20the%20lady%20he%20wishes%20to%20woo%20has%20far%20more%20important%20things%20on%20her%20mind)%20is%20eclipsed%20by%20the%20aura%20that%20surrounds%20Wing%20Commander%20Tejas%20Gill%20(Ranaut).%20She%20is%20mobbed%20by%20autograph-hunting%20girls%20who%20look%20right%20through%20the%20preening%20crooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20in%20a%20metafictional%20sense%2C%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20film%20%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%20is.%20Nobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20steal%20the%20heroine's%20thunder%20here.%20This%20is%20a%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20show%20all%20the%20way%20and%20that%20is%20the%20film's%20biggest%20undoing.%20There%20isn't%20a%20single%20fleeting%20moment%20-%20forget%20an%20entire%20sequence%20-%20in%20Tejas%20in%20which%20the%20lead%20performer%20is%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERanaut%20was%20infinitely%20better%20as%20Rani%20Lakshmibai%20(in%20%3Ci%3EManikarnika%3A%20The%20Queen%20of%20Jhansi%3C%2Fi%3E)%20than%20she%20is%20as%20an%20intrepid%20Air%20Force%20pilot.%20That%2C%20as%20is%20obvious%2C%20is%20saying%20a%20lot.%20The%20character%20she%20plays%2C%20all%20spunk%20and%20no%20substance%2C%20has%20a%20single%20dimension.%20She%20knows%20no%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20days%20in%20the%20Air%20Force%20academy%20to%20the%20risky%20mission%20she%20undertakes%20in%20order%20to%20save%20an%20Indian%20spy%20held%20hostage%20in%20Mir%20Ali%20town%20in%20Pakistan's%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province%2C%20Tejas%20Gill%20is%20a%20fount%20of%20uncommon%20intelligence%20and%20unshakeable%20confidence.%20So%2C%20the%20character%20has%20no%20arc%20to%20speak%20of.%20She%20begins%20where%20she%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejas%20Gill's%20supportive%20parents%20pop%20up%20in%20a%20few%20scenes%20but%20the%20two-hour%20film%20has%20no%20space%20for%20the%20story%20of%20the%20protagonist's%20growing%20up%20years.%20This%20ain't%20no%20%3Ci%3EGunjan%20Saxena%3A%20The%20Kargil%20Girl%3C%2Fi%3E.%20All%20that%20Tejas%20lets%20on%20is%20that%20the%20girl%20made%20up%20her%20mind%20about%20becoming%20a%20fighter%20pilot%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%20named%20India's%20fighter%20aircraft%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20female-led%20film%20touches%20upon%20the%20gender%20theme%20all%20right%2C%20but%20only%20cursorily.%20The%20men%20take%20a%20backseat%20as%20two%20girls%20lead%20the%20charge%20in%20the%20climactic%20sequences.%20That%20is%20the%20point%20that%20the%20film%20tries%20to%20make%20with%20all%20its%20might%20but%20muffs%20up%20its%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%20plunges%20straight%20into%20a%20sortie%20that%20Tejas%20makes%20in%20the%20company%20of%20Afiya%20(Anshul%20Chauhan%2C%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20cast%20who%20comes%20anywhere%20making%20an%20impression)%20to%20rescue%20an%20Air%20Force%20officer%20whose%20plane%20has%20crashed%20in%20the%20sea%20and%20his%20body%20has%20washed%20up%20on%20a%20prohibited%20island%20inhabited%20by%20the%20protected%20Sentinelese%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejas%20refuses%20to%20back%20off%20despite%20orders%20from%20higher-ups%20and%20pulls%20off%20a%20daring%20rescue%20act%2C%20shaking%20off%20an%20attack%20by%20the%20tribals%20in%20the%20process.%20She%20is%20struck%20by%20arrows.%20But%20that%20is%20no%20more%20than%20a%20professional%20hazard%20that%20is%20shrugged%20off%20without%20much%20ado.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUN6ZNUgPsPk%3Fsi%3DC3Lb3LorFprRyeyr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20bold%20and%20selfless%20effort%2C%20she%20and%20Afiya%20-%20the%20name%20might%20ring%20a%20bell%20but%20her%20religious%20identity%20is%20fiercely%20guarded%20-%20face%20an%20internal%20inquiry.%20But%20since%20it%20is%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20who%20is%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%2C%20you%20know%20that%20she%20is%20going%20to%20sail%20through%20unscathed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20that%20is%20the%20level%20at%20which%20Tejas%20flies.%20Such%20are%20the%20flights%20of%20fancy%20that%20the%20exasperatingly%20listless%20film%20indulges%20in%20that%20barely%2030%20minutes%20in%2C%20it%20turns%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20slog%20that%20is%20tough%20to%20sit%20through.%20Somebody%20says%2C%20%3Ci%3EHum%20uddte%20uddte%20jaayenge%2C%20desh%20ke%20kaam%20aayenge%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20protagonist%20takes%20that%20to%20heart.%20There%20is%20no%20stopping%20her%20from%20here%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Tejas%20sits%20at%20the%20controls%20of%20her%20first%20solo%20trial%20sortie%2C%20the%20instructor%20asks%20her%20what%20she%20can%20see.%20The%20runway%2C%20she%20replies.%20Look%20harder%2C%20the%20man%20says.%20The%20lady%20pauses%20and%20pipes%20up%3A%20I%20can%20see%20the%20road%20that%20will%20help%20me%20serve%20the%20nation.%20Spot%20on!%20She%20is%20ready%20for%20bigger%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20never%20is.%20It%20crams%20in%20everything%20that%20you%20would%20expect%20from%20a%20drama%20of%20this%20nature.%20In%202008%20Mumbai%2C%20terrorists%20interrupt%20a%20cosy%20family%20dinner.%20A%20shrieking%2C%20smirking%20mastermind%20harboured%20by%20Pakistan%20wants%20to%20ensure%20the%20barbadi%20of%20Hindustan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20look%20out%20for%20a%20ferocious%20executioner%20nicknamed%20Sar%20Qalam%20(meaning%20the%20act%20of%20decapitation)%20because%20of%20his%20proficiency%20at%20slitting%20the%20throats%20of%20hostages.%20But%20not%20to%20worry%2C%20the%20enemy%20soldiers%20that%20the%20protagonist%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20are%20a%20bunch%20of%20bumbling%2C%20easy-to-hoodwink%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20there%20is%20a%20spanking%20new%20temple%20that%20faces%20the%20threat%20of%20an%20attack%20from%20three%20jihadists%20who%20sneak%20in%20to%20sabotage%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20grand%20edifice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELogic%20is%20lost%20in%20the%20deafening%20din%20of%20the%20combat%20aircraft.%20%3Ci%3ETejas%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20film%20that%20flies%20into%20rough%20weather%20from%20the%20word%20go%20and%20never%20manages%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20it.%20An%20air%20combat%20thriller%20has%20never%20been%20so%20frustratingly%20airy-fairy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698383880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fv07j2mg8_-tejas_625x300_27_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftejas-review-an-air-combat-thriller-has-never-been-so-frustratingly-airy-fairy-1-star-4518180%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tejas%20Review%3A%20The%20film%20comes%20as%20a%20complete%20cropper%20-%20it%20is%20a%20dead-on-arrival%20cinematic%20consignment%20that%20does%20no%20justice%20at%20all%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20or%20the%20medium.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftejas-review-an-air-combat-thriller-has-never-been-so-frustratingly-airy-fairy-1-star-451