%3D%5C%22wp-image-333024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20fort%20nestled%20in%20the%20farmland%20surrounding%20it.%20Picture%20courtesy%3A%20Krutarthsinh%20Jadeja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20grow%20tomatoes%2C%20brinjal%2C%20gourds%2C%20okra%2C%20methi%2C%20%3Cem%3Echoli%20falli%2C%20gavar%20falli%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20onion%2C%20coriander%2C%20mango%2C%20Chikoo%2C%20and%20coconuts.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F218884%2Fbengaluru-couple-grow-organic-vegetable-balcony-zero-waste-tips-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetables%20are%20used%20in%20the%20meals%20%3C%2Fa%3Eprepared%20for%20both%20the%20school%20and%20the%20homestay%20for%20two%20days%20a%20week.%20The%20rest%20comes%20from%20the%20village%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98In%20Kutch%2C%20the%20tourist%20season%20is%20less%20than%20one-third%20of%20a%20year.%20Though%20tourism%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20recent%20decade%2C%20there%20was%20once%20a%20gap%20between%20the%20demand%20and%20supply%2C%20which%20the%20tourism%20department%20of%20the%20state%20tried%20to%20bridge%20with%20seasonal%20camps%20near%20the%20Rann%20of%20Kutch%2C%20and%20at%20times%20in%20Mandvi.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20pricing%20is%20not%20fair%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krutarthsinh%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20premium%20that%20a%20guest%20is%20paying%20to%20several%20hotels%20and%20resorts%20near%20the%20Rann%2C%20Bhuj%2C%20Mandvi%2C%20and%20Dholavira%2C%20going%20small%2C%20feasible%20and%20viable%20with%20homestays%20is%20the%20answer%20at%20the%20moment%20in%20my%20opinion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Darbargadh%20of%20Devpur%20is%20now%20also%20listed%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20%26amp%3B%20Cultural%20Heritage%20(INTACH)%20for%20its%20architectur