en%2C%20the%20summer%20camp%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20days%20at%20the%20summer%20camp%20looked%20like%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20at%20the%20camp%20would%20see%20around%2030%20students%2C%20aged%20between%204%20and%2012%2C%20with%20teachers%20and%20volunteers.%20The%20sessions%20would%20change%20every%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20would%20cover%20music%2C%20art%2C%20drama%2C%20story-telling%20and%20so%20on.%20Sometimes%20experts%20in%20various%20fields%20would%20give%20a%20talk%20on%20their%20subjects%20or%20coach%20the%20children%20in%20the%20art%20of%20miming%2C%20music%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20herself%20would%20write%20plays%2C%20often%20based%20on%20mythology%2C%20and%20direct%20the%20children%20in%20them.%20Recalling%20one%20such%20play%2C%20Jayshree%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20first%20teachers%20to%20join%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20story%20revolved%20around%20the%20River%20Cauvery%20from%20its%20birth%20in%20Coorg%20to%20joining%20the%20sea.%20The%20play%20would%20weave%20in%20the%20cultures%20and%20description%20of%20the%20places%20en%20route.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave%2C%20the%20participants%20would%20be%20treated%20to%20a%20special%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eprasadam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20prepared%20in%20the%20house.%20Savitri%2C%20who%20has%20been%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20help%20for%2035%20years%2C%20also%20helped%20in%20the%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESrimathi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20teachers%2C%20recollects%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20uncle%20(Mr%20Iyengar)%20pitching%20in%20some%20times%20to%20prepare%20some%20special%20food%20like%20Pizza.%20He%20would%20make%20it%20from%20scratch.%20Once%20he%20was%20preparing%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20bonda%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20I%20was%20helping%20him%20roll%20the%20potatoes.%20I%20remember%20him%20telling%20me%20to%20make%20them%20big%20enough%20so%20that%2