aunched%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20April%202022%20where%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20rejuvenate%20and%20develop%2075%20water%20bodies%20in%20each%20and%20every%20district%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20approach%20of%20building%20new%20water%20bodies%2C%20dams%20and%20canals%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20ecologically%20and%20environmentally%20damaging%20and%20often%20leads%20to%20large%20scale%20displacement%20of%20the%20locals%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20500%20water%20bodies%20were%20rejuvenated%20with%20financial%20support%20from%20NITI%20Aayog.%20Currently%2C%20pilot%20projects%20are%20ongoing%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20a%20view%20to%20extending%20this%20to%20all%20its%20aspirational%20districts%20and%20regions%20that%20are%20water%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20614px)%20100vw%2C%20614px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.23-1_11zon-1697802253.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20senior%20Maharashtra%20state%20government%20official%20says%20that%20drought%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20nemesis%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so%20since%20he%20has%20been%20posted%20and%20based%20there.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.23-1_11zon-1697802253.jpeg%20614w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.23-1_11zon-1697802253-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-10.00.23-1_11zon-1697802253-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%