%20our%20place%2C%20and%20we%20have%20hosted%20at%20least%20500%20people%20since%202016%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAjit%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20visiting%20the%20place%20with%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%20now%2C%20shares%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20stay%20at%20Tanhau.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20is%20surreal%20and%20I%20am%20not%20exaggerating%20when%20I%20say%20that%20it%20is%20the%20best%20experience%20I%20have%20ever%20had.%20It%20is%20so%20peaceful%20and%20quiet%3B%20it%20teaches%20you%20the%20importance%20of%20slow%20living.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20very%20sustainable%20setup.%20It%20feels%20good%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20travelling%20and%20not%20leaving%20a%20carbon%20footprint%20behind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20teach%20my%20son%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20nature%20and%20this%20homestay%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20participated%20in%20the%20project%20with%20a%20school%20near%20the%20homestay%20where%20we%20tried%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20plastic%20and%20its%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20promote%20slow%20and%20responsible%20travel%2C%20the%20homestay%20hosts%20unique%20activities%20to%20engage%20the%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20walking%20safaris%20in%20the%20buffer%20forest%2C%20which%20is%20an%20amazing%20and%20unique%20experience%20in%20itself.%20Of%20course%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20safari%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20jeep%2C%20but%20on%20a%20walking%20safari%2C%20you%20can%20observe%20nature%20and%20animals%20closely%2C%20without%20emitting%20any%20carbon.%20We%20also%20organise%20village%20walks%20and%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20ongoing%20village%20festivals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20guest%2C%20Avika%20Sood%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20silence%20in%20the%20place%20is%20rejuvenating.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20the%20homestay%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20have%20visited%20it%20a%20few%20times.%20The%20place%20is%20offbeat%20and%20unique.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20wildlife%20and%20animal%20kingdom%2C%20and%20Sunando%20is%20a%20walking%20library%20in%20that%20sense.%20He%20is%20very%20passionate%20about%20his%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanhau%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20guests%20at%20their%20mud%20homestay.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanhau%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20guests%20at%20their%20mud%20homestay.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Tanhau%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20I%20found%20very%20refreshing%20about%20the%20hosts%20is%20that%20they%20have%20ensured%20that%20they%20give%20more%20to%20nature%20than%20they%20take%20from%20it.%20Since%20I%20have%20been%20visiting%20them%20year%20after%20year%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20place%20grow%20into%20a%20green%20oasis.%20Every%20time%20I%20vi